name: Relics Pass
description: An artistic collective led by Jeff Cole. Membership to Metarelics and all of the exclusive benefits come from holding the Relics Pass.

asset_contract.name: Relics Pass
asset_contract.description:
The Relics Pass is brought to you by Jeff Cole and Mark Brazil, co-founders of **IKONICK** & **Sneaks of Nature**. 

The Pass sits at the core of IKONICK. Read more on the future of the Relics Pass - https://bit.ly/ikonickfu

Holding a Relics Pass will also provide utility in the Sneaks of Nature ecosystem, a franchise from the mind of Cole. 

Learn More - http://www.sneaksofnature.xyz

**Relic Reserves**: 1000 piece collections that are created or curated by Jeff Cole, provided to our Relics Pass holders twice yearly for free or at a highly discounted price. 

Next Collection: Shortstache™, launching this Holiday Season. 

https://www.instagram.com/shortstache/?hl=en

Verify your pass in Discord to check out the Relic Room, attend a Speaker Series with top tier entrepreneurs, or just hang with the crew. Be sure to select your favorite pop-tart flavor on the way in. 

Cole - http://www.instagram.com/cole/?hl=en

IKONICK - http://ikonick.com
